      "187 Resume Action Verbs That Make Recruiters Actually Stop Scrolling",
    excerpt:
      "The verbs you choose determine whether your achievements sound impressive or invisible. Here is the complete categorized list that transforms dull duty descriptions into compelling impact statements.",
    author: "Anand",
    date: "May 8, 2026",
    category: "Resume Writing",
    readTime: "13 min read",
